{"tid":1390411,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"自由閪吧 上線啦","createTime":"2019-07-31T06:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T18:12:00.000Z","uid":78857,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"19174de6d1a9d398da3b3face38015e0167326b3","tid":1390411,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:40:40.000Z","msg":"個GROUP琴日開左暫時有1300人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385263\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385263</a><br />\n名VOTE完,暫時改左叫 &lt;&lt;自由閪吧&gt;&gt;<br />\n希望更多人加入  任何意見可以提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸有龐大五毛集團係FaceBook, 討論區 <br />\n抹黑示威者 指鹿為馬 盲目撐警<br />\n令到好多特別係中年 唔識睇其他資訊ge人<br />\n唔知事實 令風向轉<br />\n我承認自己垃圾去唔到前線<br />\n但睇到d人不停抹黑示威者 個心好痛<br />\n自己不停係fb個d留言澄清 <br />\n但係有時真係唔夠人 特別係藍絲多ge group<br />\n希望grp埋一班去唔到前線ge人 一齊去反擊返5毛 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">澄清事實<br />\n還原真相<br />\n捉拿翻牆<br />\n遣返五毛<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n    自由閪吧<br />\n    五毛死全家</span><br />\nTG Grp Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkkingbar\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkkingbar&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=8067681e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkkingbar</a>"},{"pid":"f5d26848d36821c04f0834f5fcb5da5711b11177","tid":1390411,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:40:52.000Z","msg":"自推100次"},{"pid":"b7d6544aae2aa0d98b11bef2a041c9d39ed7418e","tid":1390411,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:42:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4663dd293f11e82bd4045eab1cc8e1eb6a42ed12","tid":1390411,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:42:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e832c478520b7c4aa01c6126db10f7f3909daa6","tid":1390411,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6e28d16411ef14b2f5cb00720b101da5a2fbb4d","tid":1390411,"uid":78857,"